53:36.500 --> 53:40.500
Yvonne, why are you so cold with me?

53:40.500 --> 53:43.500
Because you are to marry Alan Lwellin.

53:43.500 --> 53:47.500
Yvonne, I do not wish to marry Alan Lwellin.

53:47.500 --> 53:49.500
