53:49.500 --> 53:53.500
It is you who I wish to marry Alan Lwellin.

53:54.500 --> 53:56.500
Your father is Lord of the manor now.

53:56.500 --> 53:59.500
He will never allow you to marry someone who works on the land.

53:59.500 --> 54:01.500
I don't care about my father's wishes.

54:01.500 --> 54:03.500
I will marry you.

54:03.500 --> 54:06.500
