54:06.500 --> 54:08.500
No, it isn't.

54:08.500 --> 54:10.500
We will go away from here.

54:10.500 --> 54:11.500
Go away.

54:11.500 --> 54:13.500
Where can we go?

54:13.500 --> 54:14.500
And how will we live?

54:14.500 --> 54:16.500
We can find someone.

54:16.500 --> 54:18.500
I will not marry you.

54:18.500 --> 54:19.500
Go away.

54:19.500 --> 54:20.500
Where can we go?

54:20.500 --> 54:22.500
And how will we live?

