54:38.500 --> 54:41.500
In that case, we must go away.

54:41.500 --> 54:42.500
When?

54:42.500 --> 54:43.500
Soon.

54:43.500 --> 54:45.500
They want me to marry on my 17th birthday.

54:45.500 --> 54:47.500
In June, we have time.

54:47.500 --> 54:49.500
And I have a plan.

54:59.500 --> 55:02.500
My Lord Edward, this is a fine feast.

55:02.500 --> 55:04.500
Thank you, Chloe.

55:04.500 --> 55:08.500
Will you make the announcement of the marriage dates this evening?

55:08.500 --> 55:10.500
Indeed, I will.

55:10.500 --> 55:14.500
Lord Edward, I think it would be a fine idea.

55:14.500 --> 55:18.500
If the wedding took place sooner rather than later.

55:18.500 --> 55:20.500
Really?

55:20.500 --> 55:21.500
