55:21.500 --> 55:25.500
Well, I have heard rumours that Dorothy is...

55:25.500 --> 55:28.500
Well, how can I say?

55:28.500 --> 55:30.500
Very friendly.

55:30.500 --> 55:32.500
We're the young man in the village.

55:32.500 --> 55:34.500
A young man in the village?

55:34.500 --> 55:35.500
Who is he?

55:35.500 --> 55:39.500
A farm hand named Yvonne Turner.

55:39.500 --> 55:41.500
Yvonne Turner.

55:41.500 --> 55:42.500
I know the boy.

55:42.500 --> 55:44.500
He has worked on my land.

55:44.500 --> 55:45.500
Yes.

55:45.500 --> 55:47.500
He has worked on my land also.

55:47.500 --> 55:49.500
