55:49.500 --> 55:52.500
It is only something I have heard.

55:52.500 --> 55:59.500
Perhaps we should consider holding the wedding ceremony sooner than Dorothy's 17th birthday.

55:59.500 --> 56:00.500
Indeed.

56:00.500 --> 56:03.500
The wedding must take place as soon as possible.

56:03.500 --> 56:06.500
Let us say, Saturday week.

56:06.500 --> 56:07.500
Ten days from now.

56:07.500 --> 56:10.500
This is a fine idea, my Lord.

56:10.500 --> 56:13.500
I will make the announcement now.

56:13.500 --> 56:16.500
Ladies and gentlemen.

56:16.500 --> 56:22.500
Ladies and gentlemen, I trust that you find my humble feast to your liking.

56:22.500 --> 56:23.500
Oh, yeah.

56:23.500 --> 56:25.500
Oh, yes.

56:25.500 --> 56:34.500
I wish to take this opportunity to announce that the marriage of my daughter, Dorothy to Alan Schlewellen,

56:34.500 --> 56:39.500
the son of my friend, Schlewellen, will take place here at Plasté in ten days.

56:40.500 --> 56:42.500
