56:52.500 --> 56:57.500
Tonight, I want you to go to the village and I want you to take this bag.

56:57.500 --> 56:58.500
What is it?

56:58.500 --> 56:59.500
Look inside.

56:59.500 --> 57:02.500
I want you to take this bag.

57:02.500 --> 57:07.500
I want you to go to the village and I want you to take this bag.

57:07.500 --> 57:08.500
