57:09.500 --> 57:12.500
Oh, goodness, Miss Dorothy.

57:12.500 --> 57:14.500
These are all your jewels.

57:14.500 --> 57:17.500
What do you wish me to do with them?

57:17.500 --> 57:21.500
I want you to take the jewels to Ivan Turner's house.

57:21.500 --> 57:23.500
To Ivan's house?

57:23.500 --> 57:24.500
