57:24.500 --> 57:27.500
Please don't ask any questions.

57:27.500 --> 57:34.500
I want you to tell Ivan to meet me where the road from Plastég meets the road to Mold.

57:34.500 --> 57:39.500
Near the well, tell him to meet me there tomorrow night at midnight.

57:39.500 --> 57:43.500
Miss Dorothy, what are you thinking of?

57:43.500 --> 57:47.500
